[Guest]: had things ranging from smart investor on

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.000
[Guest]: stock markets to the strategist

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.000
[Guest]: on management. This is early to mid-90s.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:38.000
[Guest]: This would be

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.000
[Guest]: 80, yeah, that's right.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.000
[Guest]: And you had to find people

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.000
[Guest]: for that to staff this and you needed

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:46.000
[Guest]: people who are really, really bright because

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:48.000
[Guest]: you needed to go into new areas that

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:50.000
[Guest]: had not been covered in the

