[Guest]: into Europe. We know

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:44.000
[Guest]: that the earliest science of modern humans

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:46.000
[Guest]: in Europe is around 45,000

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:48.000
[Guest]: years ago or so. So

